Dustin Nguyen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dustin_Nguyen 0 Dustin Nguyen (born September 17, 1962) is an American actor, director, writer, and martial artist. He is best known for his roles as Harry Truman Ioki on 21 Jump Street, and as Johnny Loh on V.I.P. In Films, he's known for starring in Little Fish, The Doom Generation and The Rebel.
